{"tid":2368603,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[8PM][推到完場] 第43屆十大中文金曲","createTime":"2021-01-16T10:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T13:28:39.000Z","uid":1706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"78c47349632dac76ff424914486b745d9b317150","tid":2368603,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:37:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://app7.rthk.hk/special/goldsong2020/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp7.rthk.hk%2Fspecial%2Fgoldsong2020%2Findex.php&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyL3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=59cf9981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app7.rthk.hk/special/goldsong2020/index.php</a><br />\n第43屆十大中文金曲 ‧ 音樂說》特備節目將於2021年1月16日晚上8時舉行<br />\n收聽直播：<br />\n香港電台第二台（FM 94.8 －96.9）<br />\n流動程式RTHK Mine (聲音)<br />\n<br />\n收看直播：<br />\n港台電視31<br />\n香港電台網站 <a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyL3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=17839189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/</a><br />\n流動程式RTHK Screen (視像)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n音樂─我們共通的語言。<br />\n音樂說─我們共鳴的故事。<br />\n2020年，一場疫症使世界休止、把人們隔離。幸有音樂不止息，我們仍可憑歌寄意。<br />\n香港電台以樂壇盛事─【第43屆十大中文金曲】，向一眾音樂創作人及歌手致意，藉以嘉許他們在這樣艱難的大環境下，仍然堅持創作上乘音樂、守護本地中文流行樂壇，讓音樂說故事。"},{"pid":"64e8881b0060c5311433848b519e438c0f1efbab","tid":2368603,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d926c2bd33d607c2d25192ecd9fcc99070d70299","tid":2368603,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:38:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b4fe1813ff5388889bc69f27571e69adacc7b80b","tid":2368603,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:39:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a808ce63cb523cf4e63adac5ccf8b4225e61d95","tid":2368603,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{